author: Steve
title: Steve
text:
I am a techy and VERY leary of stuff, especially since there are a lot of scams out there. That being said I called and asked my questions and given answers that seemed to be ok, but I was still leary. I then proceeded to order my windows 10 cd key and once I entered all the credit card info and hit enter, I was amazed and shocked at 1: how fast it was, it was almost instant and 2: the key actually worked and was legit.
I am currently running windows 10 with the key I bought and could not be happier.
I would now trust to buy from this place a cd key for games or windows.
